  Version bump

  20 Mar 2013; Christian Birchinger <joker@gentoo.org>
  -files/razercfg-0.16-pidlogfix.patch, -razercfg-0.17.ebuild,
  -razercfg-0.17_p20111028.ebuild:
  Remove old versions and patches

  05 Feb 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  razercfg-0.19_p20121013.ebuild:
  Stop using $(get_libdir) for installing udev rules since /lib/udev is the
  correct udevdir as defined by udev.eclass

  06 Jan 2013; Zac Medico <zmedico@gentoo.org> razercfg-0.19_p20121013.ebuild:
  Use snapshot from upstream gitweb, since the current one is unfetchable (bug
  #445228).

